description._content: Original Caption: A Stormy Sky Gives the Camera a Clear View of the Clouds of Silt in the Waters Off Saddle Bunch Keys in the Lower Florida Keys Silt Occurs Naturally in the Formation of Coral Reefs, But the Amount Shown Here Could Only Be Produced by the Extensive Dredging of the Land Developers.
